	<h1 class="title">三年后，Google 放弃挑战煤炭的原因揭晓</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/4779/small/4779.jpg?1418257395" alt="">
					</span>
